{"tid":298872,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(嚴選)一人N間好嘅ig shop","createTime":"2017-06-26T15:24:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T07:36:55.000Z","uid":117080,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f74c0908542f612b86e359064d0cc1dadd939da8","tid":298872,"uid":117080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:24:15.000Z","msg":"前排有post講啲唔好嘅ig shop<br />\n唔次大家有無真心覺得心水好嘅ig shop呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲貨係咪淘寶就其次，有啲覺得啲貨夠特別、態度好嘅、有心思等等，都可以開心share下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我先(排名不分先後):<br />\n1. nippon_cc (代購黎講個價開到好評，食水唔深，款式又夠多)<br />\n<br />\n2. annekasilverjewelry (自製銀器，未係入面買過，但留意左一排準備買黎送比人，好似幾高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n3. wood.n.fly (啲衫係自己設計，好特別，唔係淘貨，買過2件衫質地都好好，店主服務態度好，有交帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n4. island_workbench (島中坊研！佢地設計嘅野簡約得黎好特別，勁中意佢地個三用袋，自己買左2個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n有新發現再加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9df356a274d1761fae8ea913912dbed2c178621","tid":298872,"uid":107294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:37:23.000Z","msg":"先去我舊po黑店ig 排除下再討論"},{"pid":"b581b74f471fc36ec6f2ce114aa7c0913e126607","tid":298872,"uid":117080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:44:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先去我舊po黑店ig 排除下再討論</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大約睇過，已排除 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb46554bc23d1ae203dd332861e678d14a60cfa8","tid":298872,"uid":117080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T16:13:56.000Z","msg":"Hi 有無人未訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69db4d8d661fe828d4550bd4c37679bedb802e8a","tid":298872,"uid":60412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"